  "title": "去海边",
  "titleEn": "Going to the Beach",
  "emoji": "🏖️",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "text": "夏天去海边玩真开心。沙滩软软的，海水凉凉的。",
      "translation": "Going to the beach in summer is so fun. The sand is soft, the sea water is cool."
    },
    {
      "text": "我在沙滩上捡贝壳。有白色的、有粉色的，真漂亮。",
      "translation": "I pick up shells on the beach. There are white ones and pink ones, so pretty."
    }
  ],
